recorded another way to remove
the poison on another tome:

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:19,800
blood for blood...

6
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:22,480
a life...

7
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,240
for a life.

8
00:00:29,360 --> 00:00:30,720
From now on,

9
