17
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,920
Alright.

18
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,960
Hen Xiang!

19
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,160
Your Majesty.

20
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,760
Nian.

21
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,600
Chou.

22
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,880
Go now!

23
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,560
Nian.

24
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,640
Chou.

25
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:23,560
You've done very well.

26
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,320
And you've protected...

27
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:28,600
both of the children well.

28
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,240
Chou.

29
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,040
I'll find you again...

30
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,120
in my next life.

31
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:51,240
<i>I regret the one mistake
that I made so much.</i>

32
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:55,440
<i>All hopes are lost,
how do I start over?</i>

33
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:57,400
In your next life,

34
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,840
don't meet me anymore.

35
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:04,680
<i>I blamed the mistake
that happened too soon.</i>

36
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,280
Wu Chou.

37
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:51,880
<i>It never ends, love will fade.</i>

38
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:56,160
<i>The blossoms fall,
and I waited in silence.</i>

39
00:06:56,440 --> 00:07:00,640
<i>I cling onto the past
despite the pains.</i>

40
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:04,800
<i>I won't let our love be a regret.</i>

41
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:09,320
<i>Live without sorrow,
die without any hate.</i>

42
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:13,720
<i>This is the leniency that
you've shown me.</i>

43
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,840
Nian.

44
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,600
Nian.

45
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:26,720
<i>Live without sorrow,
die without any hate.</i>

46
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,320
<i>This is the leniency that
you've shown me.</i>

47
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:32,120
Don't worry.

48
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,880
I promise you.

49
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:36,640
I'll take good care of your child.

50
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,400
<i>Wu You.</i>

51
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,720
<i>From now on,
we don't owe each other anymore.</i>

52
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:48,120
<i>Luckily, a ray of light has
shone into my life...</i>

53
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:51,160
<i>before I'm totally swallowed up
by dark hatred.</i>

54
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,760
Father.

55
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,320
Father.

56
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,800
Father.

