-Father.
-Father.

61
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:38,360
Father.

62
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,920
Father.

63
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:44,040
I know that my life
is coming to an end.

64
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,520
So, I'm holding on
to my last breath...

65
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:50,080
to wait for both of you here.

66
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,880
All these sins.

67
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,920
They should be bore by me alone.

68
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,600
Back then,

69
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:05,200
because of my wild ambition
to rebuilt the country,

70
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:09,880
I had played with other's feelings.

71
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,320
And the price I have to pay...

72
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:17,640
is to see both of you brothers
destroying each other.

73
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,440
Father.

74
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,760
Crown prince.

75
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,800
Wu Chou.

76
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,240
And your children...

77
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,680
Father.

78
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:34,360
have become the innocent victims.

79
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:38,000
Both of you...

80
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,560
have to remember the mistake I made.

81
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:45,600
In the future,

82
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,960
don't fail to live up to...

83
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:51,360
the people of our country.

84
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:53,160
-Father.
-Father.

85
