Your karma!

94
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,240
Cut the nonsense.

95
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:55,080
Where is Man Yao?

96
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,160
You have...

97
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,880
searched the whole palace for her...

98
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,680
but you couldn't find her.

99
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,360
It means that...

100
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,880
she is dead.

101
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,480
Wu You, we have searched the
whole palace from the inside out.

102
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:18,160
And we couldn't find Consort Rong Le.

103
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:20,400
But Xiao Sha is still looking for her.

104
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,640
I don't believe you.

105
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,240
Give her back to me.

106
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,920
Man Yao.

107
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,320
Man Yao.

108
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,000
Brother Qi.

109
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:31,640
Wait for me.

110
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,120
Brother Qi.

111
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,800
Wait for me.

112
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,000
Stop right there.

113
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,320
You...

114
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,480
Why are you still alive?

115
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:49,200
How is it possible that my Qi is dead?

116
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:52,040
Although he has contacted
the Destined Poison,

117
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:55,240
for the past 20 years and more,

118
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:59,840
I had carefully used the most
valuable medicine to prolong his life.

119
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:02,440
You must be...

120
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:06,640
the reason behind his death.

121
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,520
Brother Qi is dead?

122
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,040
Brother Qi.

123
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:17,160
Why are you still here?

124
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:19,840
Are you...

125
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,640
afraid that your mother
will suspect you?

126
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,560
Are you afraid that your mother...

127
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:28,160
will stop Ke from getting rid
of the poison inside me?

128
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:32,480
You have already given
your blood and life to me.

129
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,800
Now, you even use your dead body...

130
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,560
to protect me.

131
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,640
No.

132
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,720
That is impossible.

133
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,640
That is impossible.

134
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,680
Brother Qi.

135
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:49,840
I'm sorry.

136
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,680
I shouldn't have forgotten about you.

137
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:57,080
How could I have forgotten about you?

138
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,840
Then, why don't you...

139
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,880
die together with him?

140
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:04,280
You are not worthy for all the things
that Qi had done for you.

141
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:20,960
You...

142
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:25,160
should have already been dead
when you contacted...

143
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,960
the Scorpion Toxin.

144
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:29,720
If Qi had not saved you...

145
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:31,680
by putting the medicine...

146
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:34,240
in your snacks to protect your heart,

147
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:37,160
you wouldn't have gotten off
with just white hair.

148
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:39,600
But in order to save you,

149
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:42,160
do you know what
punishment he received?

150
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:45,120
You are unworthy of being a mother.

151
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:50,120
The things that I did...

152
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,280
were nothing.

153
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,840
The physical pain Qi felt...

154
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,320
is nothing...

155
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:02,480
compared to the heartache
he felt when he knew that...

156
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,840
you had fallen in love
with Zongzheng Wu You.

157
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,480
In order to save you,

158
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:10,680
he gave you to others
with his own hands.

159
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,440
He had to put his pride
in his pocket...

160
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:16,720
and he had to put up with
your hatred towards him.

161
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:22,600
No.

162
00:17:24,320 --> 00:17:26,480
It's all because of you.

163
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:28,640
Fu Yuan.

164
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:31,480
My father had indeed hurt you before.

165
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:35,720
But my mother had forgiven you.

166
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,440
Wu Chou had respected
and taken care of you.

167
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:41,800
Man Yao had helped you before.

168
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,600
And the people from
several countries...

169
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:46,480
had protected and served you.

170
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:49,200
But because of your own hatred,

171
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,800
you have hurt so many people.

172
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:53,960
And you almost...

173
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:56,840
incite war between us few countries.

174
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,160
Reprisal breeds reprisal.

175
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:00,920
But the people are innocent.

176
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:03,840
When you willingly let yourself
be swallowed up by hatred,

177
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:09,160
-you should have expected this ending.
-Everything that all of you did...

178
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:11,280
is fake and insincere!

179
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,120
I have nothing now.

180
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,560
<i>Everything that you see
can be fabricated.</i>

181
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,000
<i>So, you have to believe in your heart.</i>

182
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:15,200
<i>I'm the one who wishes for
your happiness the most in this world.</i>

183
00:19:18,760 --> 00:19:21,760
<i>What I can promise you now is,
your child will be fine.</i>

184
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:23,240
<i>Your child will be safe.</i>

185
00:19:23,720 --> 00:19:24,920
<i>I won't lie to you.</i>

186
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:27,320
<i>I promise to neutralise
your poison for sure, Man.</i>

187
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:31,240
<i>I just hope that you can
trust me for one last time.</i>

188
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:44,120
<i>Man.</i>

189
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:45,520
<i>Since...</i>

190
00:19:45,840 --> 00:19:47,840
<i>I won't be able to
bring you happiness,</i>

191
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:50,040
<i>I should just...</i>

192
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:52,680
<i>give you my blessings.</i>

193
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,400
<i>Man,</i>

194
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:02,040
<i>don't forgive me.</i>

195
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,880
<i>Continue to hate me like this.</i>

196
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:08,080
<i>Because, when the people
you hate leave you,</i>

197
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:11,440
<i>you won't be too sad about it.</i>

198
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,040
" Here lies Zongzheng Wu Chou
and Qin Xiang "

199
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,600
Wu Chou.

200
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,840
Mother had taught me this song.

201
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:07,760
I hope that you'll like it.

202
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:11,880
Whenever she thought
about her other lost child,

203
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:15,160
he will play this song alone.

204
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:19,200
Unfortunately,
you didn't get to hear it...

205
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:21,320
when you are still alive.

206
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:34,800
Man Yao...

207
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:37,200
is still not willing
to leave Western Qi?

208
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:40,240
Consort Rong Le is
not willing to talk much.

209
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:42,240
She just sits in the tearoom alone...

210
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:44,160
and wanders around the Cold Harem.

211
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:47,560
If that's the case,
no need to disturb her anymore.

212
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,880
All of us are not able to
blot out our past...

213
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:01,600
and the deep hatred that is
engraved in our heart.

214
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:07,080
A few years ago, I might force her
to come with me at all cost.

215
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,080
But time has changed.

216
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:13,680
Sooner or later,
we will understand that...

217
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,800
putting down things that
we are persistent on...

218
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,400
is leniency towards ourselves.

219
00:22:19,880 --> 00:22:21,000
Your Highness.

220
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:23,520
When Emperor of Qi was still alive,

221
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:25,760
he had asked you to
help him with something.

222
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,760
Greetings, Your Highness.

223
00:22:37,320 --> 00:22:39,360
When His Majesty was still alive,
he wrote this letter...

224
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:42,640
and instructed me to give it
to you and only you.

225
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:59,040
<i>Prince Li.</i>

226
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:01,040
<i>This letter represents me.</i>

227
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,040
<i>My life is going to end soon.</i>

228
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:06,560
<i>But I still have
some regrets in my life.</i>

229
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:09,080
<i>Although we are not close,</i>

230
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:10,880
<i>in this world,</i>

231
00:23:11,080 --> 00:23:13,480
<i>you are the only one
generous enough...</i>

232
00:23:13,800 --> 00:23:15,800
<i>for me to count on.</i>

233
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,400
My mother had sinned
throughout her life.

234
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:23,920
As her son,
I'll repay it with my life.

235
00:23:24,200 --> 00:23:27,560
I hope that her victims will be able
to forgive her for her crimes...

236
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,640
and let go of their hatred.

237
00:23:31,280 --> 00:23:34,400
Me and Qin Man's destiny
has ended a long time ago.

238
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:38,160
You are the only one she loves...

239
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:40,160
in this whole wide world.

240
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:44,440
I hope that you can
keep your promise...

241
00:23:44,840 --> 00:23:48,320
to respect and love her forever.

242
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,520
Western Qi is poor and weak.

243
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,400
Our people are suffering.

244
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:57,080
I'm afraid that my death will
lead to the destruction of our nation.

245
00:23:57,920 --> 00:24:01,440
I hope that you can
take care of my people...

246
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:05,000
as a benevolent ruler.

247
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:12,040
<i>I can saw you turning
your back towards me.</i>

248
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:18,760
<i>I weep for the good times
we had that was broken.</i>

249
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:26,120
<i>I have so many memories of you
but it'll never be enough.</i>

250
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:30,480
" Five years later "

251
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:40,760
<i>I tried to capture you
but I've broken your wings.</i>

252
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:47,800
<i>Separation is our only end.
I promise you with my burning heart.</i>

253
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:54,640
<i>If you are willing to
believe in this world again,</i>

254
00:24:54,960 --> 00:25:00,760
<i>please remember that...</i>

255
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:08,760
<i>I once loved you.</i>

256
00:25:09,440 --> 00:25:13,160
" Here lies Brother Rong Qi "

257
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:23,680
Xiao Sha.

258
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,760
Thank you for taking care...

259
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,760
of my brother all these years.

260
00:25:29,840 --> 00:25:31,600
If His Majesty can hear us
from the underworld,

261
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:34,240
he can definitely hear your grief.

262
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:37,240
I still feel guilty
after all these years.

263
00:25:38,080 --> 00:25:40,200
When you and His Majesty were in Chen,

264
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:42,080
His Majesty had insisted
to take you away...

265
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:45,200
because he had found the other half of
the medical book of Lone Frost Sage.

